name: Questions of Satoshi Nakamoto
description:
If the claimed current age of Satoshi (the supposed creator of Bitcoin) is 46, why do past constructed images of him? look so old? These images are actually of Dorian Prentice Satoshi Nakamoto who is currently 72 years of age as of 17 October 2021.

This is an experimental alt account of @spacegoodies in development.
